{"tid":793772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國商務部長：美國在知識產權抹黑中國","createTime":"2018-08-25T16:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T04:44:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"279fa7986418693ac131ad1970b4badeb0e7c5e4","tid":793772,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"鐘山批評美國在知識產權等抹黑中國<br />\n25.08.2018 23:30<br />\n中英經貿聯委會第13次會議昨日在北京舉行，由商務部長鐘山及英國國際貿易大臣霍理林共同主持。鐘山提及中美貿易摩擦，指美國發動貿易戰嚴重違反世貿規則，是單邊及霸淩主義，美國並在知識產權等方面抹黑中國，強調貿易戰沒有贏家，中方不願打貿易戰，但亦不怕打，將堅決捍衛國家及人民利益。霍理林表示，英方堅定支持自由貿易，反對單邊主義及貿易保護主義，希望中美通過磋商解決分歧。"},{"pid":"2794b3fedd65f26a23e36e120d61dcfd509a92f6","tid":793772,"uid":13303,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"有無第二句呀好悶呀"},{"pid":"66a54bb4370700e708ecb4208dc6624f4d3dd0fe","tid":793772,"uid":52230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"英國越黎越奶共了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bce014996e87f026853347390d002f1e165f76a","tid":793772,"uid":155732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"66a54bb4370700e708ecb4208dc6624f4d3dd0fe","tid":793772,"uid":52230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"英國越黎越奶共了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T19:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正垃圾 大英帝國既尊嚴去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28524457fdb40de6621fceb97fdd84c17838c7da","tid":793772,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2794b3fedd65f26a23e36e120d61dcfd509a92f6","tid":793772,"uid":13303,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"rep